# Datasets / large files
data/
datasets/
*.tar.gz
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar
*.gz

# --- Project docs (internal working notes) ---
# Brainstorming specs/plans and release notes are kept local-only; nothing under
# docs/ is tracked. The release workflow uses auto-generated notes, so it does
# not depend on any committed file here.
docs/

# --- Playwright UI-verification artifacts ---
# Ad-hoc screenshots captured during manual UI checks live at the repo root
# (banner-*.png, clean-*.png, step*-*.png, …) plus the Playwright MCP output
# dir. They're throwaway test artifacts — never tracked. Scoped to the root so
# real PNG assets under frontend/ etc. are unaffected.
/.playwright-mcp/
/*.png
